des: Banker News will inform you at regular intervals of shares traded by private investors at Tradegate Exchange, Europe’s leading marketplace for private investors. The long trading hours (08:00 to 22:00 CST, UTC +2) and outstanding liquidity enable us to provide an actual view of current trading activities in the securities business.
